title: #92Noon! Combine Catchup!
description: We can't be at the Combine, so we are trying to bring the Combine to us. NFL/Draft conversation features Corey Chavous and Texans vox Marc Vandermeer in the first hour...NFL reporter Adam Caplan, Draft Network analyst Jordan Reid and ESPN's Dan Orlovsky midway through...then final hour features the Birk Bit and NFL Network's Tom Pelissero!
